author: hwright
msg: FSFS: If a representation does not have a sha1 checksum, that means it is
from an older incarnation of the database, so do not include an empty checksum
and a null uniquifier in the representation string.
(representation_string): Use the existance of the sha1 checksum to determine
whether or not the sha1 should even be written.
